<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">21倍速算法，21与某数相乘时，可先将某数扩大20倍后，再加上上某数，即为其积。其口诀是：21先作20算，然后再将某数添。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">a×21=a×20+a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">36×21=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 36×21</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=36×20+36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=720+36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=756</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>